---
import DocsLayout from '../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro'
---
<DocsLayout title="BridgeAIChat Docs" description="Install, run, and troubleshoot the BridgeAIChat beta.">
  <section class="surface">
    <div class="eyebrow">Documentation</div>
    <h1>From first install to a working multi-device beta setup.</h1>
    <p class="lede">
      Start with the quickstart for the shortest path. Use the install and tooling guides when you want a cleaner
      control-host setup or a better-tuned remote device.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="section-gap grid two">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="eyebrow">Start Here</div>
      <h2>Core setup path</h2>
      <div class="doc-links">
        <a class="doc-link" href="/docs/quickstart">
          <div><strong>Quickstart</strong><span>Fastest path from fresh install to first reply.</span></div>
          <span class="doc-link-arrow">›</span>
        </a>
        <a class="doc-link" href="/docs/install/control-host">
          <div><strong>Install the control host</strong><span>Run the gateway, set Tailscale API credentials, and open the UI.</span></div>
          <span class="doc-link-arrow">›</span>
        </a>
        <a class="doc-link" href="/docs/install/agent">
          <div><strong>Install an agent device</strong><span>Configure tmux, gateway connectivity, your local AI CLI, and the built-in Bridge Helper.</span></div>
          <span class="doc-link-arrow">›</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="eyebrow">Guides</div>
      <h2>Environment-specific help</h2>
      <div class="doc-links">
        <a class="doc-link" href="/docs/tools/codex">
          <div><strong>Codex guide</strong><span>Recommended beta path and working assumptions.</span></div>
          <span class="doc-link-arrow">›</span>
        </a>
        <a class="doc-link" href="/docs/tools/claude">
          <div><strong>Claude guide</strong><span>Login, quota, and local-device caveats.</span></div>
          <span class="doc-link-arrow">›</span>
        </a>
        <a class="doc-link" href="/docs/networking/tailscale">
          <div><strong>Tailscale guide</strong><span>Tailnet input, API credentials, and private agent routing.</span></div>
          <span class="doc-link-arrow">›</span>
        </a>
        <a class="doc-link" href="/docs/troubleshooting">
          <div><strong>Troubleshooting</strong><span>Fix the most common setup and runtime failures.</span></div>
          <span class="doc-link-arrow">›</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</DocsLayout>
